{"tid":1327833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄又要賣港啦！","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T18:58:52.000Z","uid":14006,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"131f7a2b96d8f681855e834af6c580990d3d94f5","tid":1327833,"uid":14006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:47:36.000Z","msg":"雖然講明唔包括大陸，但係魔鬼在細節。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「逃犯引渡條例修訂，政府不單止無撤回，而且由張超雄重新啟動了！張超雄提出私人條例草案，提出只是適用於中華地區除了澳門和大陸之後的台灣引渡協定。即是說，這是逃犯引渡條例的收窄版，只限於台灣與香港的引渡。張超雄極度惡毒，他的私人條例草案有三點危機：<br />\n<br />\n一、這<span style=\"color: orange;\">封殺了香港社運人士流亡台灣之路</span>，令他們隨時被引渡回來香港。<br />\n<br />\n二、一旦開啟了台灣的引渡條例修訂，之後<span style=\"color: orange;\">再依次開啟澳門、大陸的修訂就變得容易</span>，因為有了先例，打破了原先條例的不引渡中國地區，日後只需要適應化就可以引渡去中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n三、這將台灣安放在中國的司法觀念之內，在法理上<span style=\"color: orange;\">妨礙台灣獨立</span>。雖然只是香港一廂情願通過，但也會妨礙國際法理，而且方便一國兩制將來在台灣實現。<br />\n<br />\n原來張超雄潛伏這麼久，現在才顯示作用。他是最惡毒的賣港賊、賣台賊。」<br />\n<br />\nfrom 陳雲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157266575662225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157266575662225&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=a541e04d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157266575662225</a>"},{"pid":"f54871551baa621a3998975b40f59c5f8384e871","tid":1327833,"uid":14087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"其實我係覺得佢蠢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過 呢條例用咩方式都唔岩 現階段"},{"pid":"7ec879670198ec0624ce3b38714eb03f303e5c0c","tid":1327833,"uid":14006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f54871551baa621a3998975b40f59c5f8384e871","tid":1327833,"uid":14087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"其實我係覺得佢蠢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過 呢條例用咩方式都唔岩 現階段"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"唔理佢蠢又好，惡毒又好，佢做嘅嘢會帶來破壞就要反對。"},{"pid":"e9ea6bf296bf80198e34b722f8a874cbb8dd802d","tid":1327833,"uid":14006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f5ec38c32fa5228ea9130a788f9a01673d1ef56","tid":1327833,"uid":14006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"淨係第一點已經對逃亡去台灣嘅義士極不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f2e3eaf173b8cd019f13c8bae9816b8e791516","tid":1327833,"uid":38654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"有線唔係咁講喎<br />\n[url]iCable <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/....../即時新聞/據指家屬致函特首倡四方案交疑犯[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2F......%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%93%9A%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%80%A1%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%A4%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%5B%2Furl%5D&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=dac51139\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2F......%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%93%9A%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%80%A1%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%A4%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%5B%2Furl%5D&h=98e35fd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/....../即時新聞/據指家屬致函特首倡四方案交疑犯[/url]</a><br />\n立法會議員楊岳橋、尹兆堅及張超雄分別提交私人草案，建議修訂《侵害人身罪》、《刑事司法管轄權條例》，及以單次個案方式移交疑犯到台灣，張超雄表示已獲律政司發出證明書。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.civicparty.hk/?q=node/8310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.civicparty.hk%2F%3Fq%3Dnode%2F8310&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=c942169d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.civicparty.hk/?q=node/8310</a><br />\n楊岳橋強調，私人草案旨在向政府提供示範框架，顯示有其他可行方法處理台灣殺人案，而無須修訂《逃犯條例》。"}]}